        "description": "Sequential compression-bending tests on six non-cannulated constructs at Laboratory 1. Specimens were tested in the order received; no randomisation of specimen assignment or blinding of measurement collection was performed. Ambient conditions were logged but not controlled to a pre-specified range. The activity followed ASTM F1717 procedural steps for loading rate and fixture geometry, and the resulting force-displacement data were used directly for QoI extraction and model comparison.",
